OL,3,CFormer councillor jailed for sexually
OL,4,Cassaulting child
OL,6,FA former councillor from
OL,7,FGloucestershire has been jailed after
OL,8,Fbeing found guilty of sexually
OL,9,Fassaulting a child.
OL,11,FPaul Ockelton, from Innsworth, near
OL,12,FGloucester, denied sexually assaulting
OL,13,Fa girl under the age of 13 but was
OL,14,Ffound guilty following a four-day
OL,15,Ftrial in March.
OL,17,FThe 60-year-old, who represented
OL,18,FInnsworth on Tewkesbury Borough
OL,19,FCouncil, was jailed for 18 months.
