OL,6,FHe was also placed on the sex
OL,7,Foffenders register for 10 years and
OL,8,Fmade the subject of a sexual harm
OL,9,Fprevention order.
OL,11,F'Shattered by his actions' - victim's
OL,12,Fmum
OL,14,FOckelton carried out his assault in
OL,15,FNovember 2021.
OL,17,FHe sat his victim on his lap and asked
OL,18,Fher "do you like this?" while he
OL,19,Fcarried out the assault, the court was
OL,20,Ftold.
