OL,3,CFormer councillor jailed for sexually
OL,4,Cassaulting child
OL,6,FOckelton denied he had touched her
OL,7,Finappropriately, claiming he had been
OL,8,Ftickling her tummy and brushing her
OL,9,Fhair, but a jury rejected his defence.
OL,11,FThe victim's mum told the court: "I am
OL,12,Fsaddened that my daughter's wellbeing
OL,13,Fand confidence has been so badly
OL,14,Fshattered by his actions.
OL,16,F"No-one has the right to touch my
OL,17,Fdaughter and it is something that will
OL,18,Faffect her for the rest of her life.
OL,19,FShe is the most amazing and beautiful
OL,20,Flittle girl."
