OL,3,CFormer councillor jailed for sexually
OL,4,Cassaulting child
OL,6,FDet Sgt Grace Craddock, of
OL,7,FGloucestershire Police, praised the
OL,8,Fgirl's bravery.
OL,10,F"The child victim in this case has
OL,11,Fbeen unbelievably brave by letting her
OL,12,Fparents know what Ockelton had done to
OL,13,Fher," she said.
OL,15,F"The strength shown by her family
OL,16,Fthroughout this difficult process too
OL,17,Fhas been incredible, and I commend
OL,18,Fthem for working with us to ensure
OL,19,FOckelton has been convicted and now
OL,20,Fsentenced for his offending."
